00:15:46,140 --> 00:15:47,620
His Majesty and Her Highness

289
00:15:48,060 --> 00:15:49,660
are in no mood for the moon.

290
00:15:52,420 --> 00:15:53,860
This afternoon,

291
00:15:54,180 --> 00:15:55,700
Her Highness went to pray for her.

292
00:15:57,060 --> 00:16:00,500
We hate Madam Zhang for her domineering.

293
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:03,420
But think about it.

294
00:16:03,420 --> 00:16:04,620
She’s also a poor person.

295
00:16:06,020 --> 00:16:08,420
Her two daughters were gone.

296
00:16:09,460 --> 00:16:10,860
Now, the Eighth Princess is also...

297
00:16:15,460 --> 00:16:16,980
I knew it would hurt.

298
00:16:18,460 --> 00:16:20,210
Now I felt how painful and scared

299
00:16:20,215 --> 00:16:21,580
I could be.

300
00:16:25,940 --> 00:16:27,100
These days,

301
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:30,700
when Huirou eats less or coughs,

302
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:32,220
I feel scared.

303
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:38,500
His Majesty worries, too.

304
00:16:40,420 --> 00:16:42,980
That day, he slept in my chamber.

305
00:16:43,660 --> 00:16:46,060
I woke up in the midnight but didn’t see him.

306
00:16:47,260 --> 00:16:47,980
It turns out that he went to

307
00:16:47,980 --> 00:16:49,900
check on Huirou.

308
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:52,300
Because Huirou had

309
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:53,860
too many iced red bayberries

310
00:16:54,340 --> 00:16:55,580
and had a stomachache.

311
00:16:56,940 --> 00:16:58,340
He didn’t say anything,

312
00:17:00,860 --> 00:17:02,300
but he was worried.

313
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:04,780
Everyone knows

314
00:17:05,100 --> 00:17:06,380
even though His Majesty spoils Madam Zhang,

315
00:17:06,460 --> 00:17:07,420
in his heart

316
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:09,420
he cares for Huirou the most.

317
00:17:10,820 --> 00:17:13,180
Madam Miao, don’t be sad.

318
00:17:14,140 --> 00:17:15,300
You’re still young.

319
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:17,980
You can still have a son for His Majesty.

320
00:17:30,695 --> 00:17:31,780
Really?

321
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:35,780
The physician said that.

322
00:17:35,940 --> 00:17:37,300
I think it’s real.

323
00:17:42,660 --> 00:17:43,660
The Eighth Princess will...

324
00:17:49,300 --> 00:17:51,020
Madam Zhang is really a poor woman.

325
00:17:51,940 --> 00:17:53,340
Don’t bother to show mercy on her.

326
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:54,980
She has got

327
00:17:54,980 --> 00:17:56,100
a backup plan.

328
00:17:56,820 --> 00:17:57,620
Look.

329
00:17:58,660 --> 00:18:00,500
His Majesty picked her maid

330
00:18:01,060 --> 00:18:01,820
as the Combing Stewardess

331
00:18:01,820 --> 00:18:03,060
at last.

332
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:08,940
Madam.

333
00:18:10,260 --> 00:18:11,940
Youwu will get better.

334
00:18:12,340 --> 00:18:13,940
Don’t be too sad.

335
00:18:17,260 --> 00:18:18,140
If you keep crying,

336
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:19,060
you’ll be ill.

337
00:18:19,060 --> 00:18:19,820
His Majesty has arrived.

338
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:23,140
Your Majesty.

339
00:18:24,540 --> 00:18:25,500
Your Majesty.

340
00:18:26,460 --> 00:18:28,340
Youwu doesn’t take in any medicine

341
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:30,260
or water.

342
00:18:35,700 --> 00:18:36,420
Be seated.

343
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:37,820
She’s feeling bad,

344
00:18:39,180 --> 00:18:40,700
but she seldom cries out.

345
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:42,580
Every time, she wipes my eyes

346
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:43,980
with her little hand.

347
00:18:47,860 --> 00:18:50,060
The physician said she had a weak heart.

348
00:18:50,740 --> 00:18:52,660
That was what they said about Chuyue.

349
00:18:53,620 --> 00:18:55,420
Chuyue and Yaoyao were gone.

350
00:18:56,420 --> 00:18:58,300
Will Youwu leave me too?

351
00:19:01,260 --> 00:19:04,660
Your Majesty, do they blame me

352
00:19:05,020 --> 00:19:06,420
because I always want to

353
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:07,860
have a son for you?

354
00:19:09,940 --> 00:19:11,420
But when I see them,

355
00:19:12,220 --> 00:19:13,540
I love them.

356
00:19:13,820 --> 00:19:15,660
I won’t exchange them

357
00:19:15,660 --> 00:19:16,860
for even ten sons.

358
00:19:17,820 --> 00:19:18,580
I know.

359
00:19:20,580 --> 00:19:21,980
They will know, too.

360
00:19:23,860 --> 00:19:25,180
As long as Youwu can get better,

361
00:19:26,020 --> 00:19:27,300
I’ll want nothing.

362
00:19:28,180 --> 00:19:29,340
She’s your daughter

363
00:19:29,340 --> 00:19:30,620
and the princess of our nation.

364
00:19:31,540 --> 00:19:32,460
I swear.

365
00:19:33,020 --> 00:19:34,380
I’ll just stay with her

366
00:19:34,380 --> 00:19:35,900
and take care of her.

367
00:19:35,900 --> 00:19:37,260
I’ll want nothing more.

368
00:19:40,700 --> 00:19:42,300
Lantiao has some purpose.

369
00:19:42,620 --> 00:19:44,220
His Majesty doesn’t like her too much.

370
00:19:44,220 --> 00:19:45,460
Yet he doesn’t hate her, either.

371
00:19:45,820 --> 00:19:47,740
She takes good care of His Majesty.

372
00:19:47,860 --> 00:19:48,780
She’s gentle and obedient.

373
00:19:49,660 --> 00:19:50,900
Gentle and obedient?

374
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:56,380
She planted on Madam Zhang last time.

375
00:19:56,940 --> 00:19:58,300
What do you mean gentle?

376
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:01,580
Then why...

377
00:20:03,180 --> 00:20:04,540
Zhang Bihan is stupid.

378
00:20:05,820 --> 00:20:07,220
She works with Xu Lantiao,

379
00:20:07,220 --> 00:20:08,380
thinking she can control Xu Lantiao

380
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:09,980
by giving her some benefits.

381
00:20:10,460 --> 00:20:13,020
She doesn’t know she’s helping an ungrateful girl.

382
00:20:15,740 --> 00:20:17,020
As for Xu Lantiao,

383
00:20:17,340 --> 00:20:19,180
she hooked up with Yang Huaimin.

384
00:20:19,980 --> 00:20:21,620
If she were an ordinary maid,

385
00:20:21,660 --> 00:20:22,780
that would be okay.

386
00:20:23,060 --> 00:20:24,500
But she’s too ambitious.

387
00:20:24,540 --> 00:20:25,700
And she isn’t good enough.

388
00:20:26,140 --> 00:20:28,580
She’ll bring ruin upon herself.

389
00:20:30,100 --> 00:20:31,540
Gu Cai’er is badly sick

390
00:20:31,620 --> 00:20:32,820
and has left the palace in advance.

391
00:20:33,060 --> 00:20:34,620
His Majesty chose Xu Lantiao

392
00:20:34,620 --> 00:20:35,700
as the Combing Stewardess

393
00:20:35,860 --> 00:20:36,980
instead of Qiuhe.

394
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:39,860
Everyone thinks

395
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:42,740
that’s because

396
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:44,380
His Majesty favors Madam Zhang

397
00:20:45,060 --> 00:20:46,260
and doesn’t want the maid Her Highness recommends.

398
00:20:48,820 --> 00:20:50,140
His Majesty is always benevolent.

399
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:51,260
Why is he

400
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:53,300
only harsh to Her Highness?

401
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:04,740
On the last Mid-autumn Festival,

402
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:09,700
Fan Xiwen drank to the moon,

403
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:12,500
talking about the clear situation

404
00:21:12,740 --> 00:21:15,140
when redundant officials were dismissed.

405
00:21:15,820 --> 00:21:16,940
= Wang Yirou, courtesy name Shengzhi =
Ouyang Yongshu

406
00:21:18,540 --> 00:21:21,460
even wrote a poem when he was half drunk.

407
00:21:22,220 --> 00:21:23,140
I...

408
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:26,380
I...

409
00:21:28,020 --> 00:21:29,780
I shouldn’t talk about state affairs now.

410
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:30,740
Let’s drink.

411
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:31,940
Let go of state affairs.

412
00:21:31,980 --> 00:21:33,660
Come on. Cheers. Come on.

413
00:21:33,860 --> 00:21:36,740
No state affairs. Let’s drink

414
00:21:36,940 --> 00:21:38,100
and talk about something romantic.

415
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:42,820
Enjoy the flowers and the moon.

416
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:53,100
♪ It’s cool in September ♪

417
00:21:54,820 --> 00:22:00,580
♪ We drink and amuse ourselves ♪

418
00:22:01,740 --> 00:22:08,225
♪ Rivers will fill a bowl ♪

419
00:22:09,260 --> 00:22:14,820
♪ And oceans will fill a full pot ♪

420
00:22:15,395 --> 00:22:19,220
♪ A full pot ♪

421
00:22:19,740 --> 00:22:21,140
Good one! Good!

422
00:22:21,500 --> 00:22:23,500
Good. Cheers.

423
00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:25,500
A full pot.

424
00:22:27,740 --> 00:22:30,020
We should propose a full pot!

425
00:22:32,020 --> 00:22:37,060
♪ I have nowhere to sleep after I’m drunk ♪

426
00:22:38,460 --> 00:22:43,460
♪ I can’t help when friends are in trouble ♪

427
00:22:44,020 --> 00:22:50,780
♪ I’ll send an emperor to support him ♪

428
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:54,100
♪ I’ll enslave even Duke of Zhou and Confucius ♪

429
00:22:54,100 --> 00:22:58,060
= Cabinet Official, Li Ding =
♪ I’ll enslave even Duke of Zhou and Confucius ♪

430
00:22:58,060 --> 00:23:00,100
♪ I’ll enslave even Duke of Zhou and Confucius ♪

431
00:23:02,675 --> 00:23:03,700
You’re drunk.

432
00:23:04,380 --> 00:23:05,500
He’s drunk. Drunk.

433
00:23:05,740 --> 00:23:07,140
Come on, everybody.

434
00:23:07,260 --> 00:23:08,180
Don’t lose your cool.

435
00:23:08,180 --> 00:23:09,220
Let’s drink.

436
00:23:09,220 --> 00:23:09,980
Don’t drink too much.

437
00:23:09,980 --> 00:23:10,940
Don’t talk about state affairs.

438
00:23:19,460 --> 00:23:20,980
I’m a Cabinet Official, Li Ding.

439
00:23:20,980 --> 00:23:22,140
I come to see Chief Xia.

440
00:23:22,860 --> 00:23:23,940
Come in, please.

441
00:23:23,940 --> 00:23:24,580
Okay.

442
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:27,715
This way.

443
00:23:32,460 --> 00:23:34,340
As you said,

444
00:23:34,660 --> 00:23:37,540
academic officials

445
00:23:37,620 --> 00:23:39,020
visited a brothel

446
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:43,140
and were destructive to the morals,

447
00:23:44,220 --> 00:23:47,100
you should tell Kaifeng Municipal Government

448
00:23:47,100 --> 00:23:48,420
or Imperial Security Agency.

449
00:23:50,020 --> 00:23:51,460
If they even

450
00:23:52,420 --> 00:23:55,660
used public funds,

451
00:23:57,260 --> 00:24:00,740
you should tell the Censorate.

452
00:24:03,260 --> 00:24:06,980
Kaifeng Municipal Government,
Imperial Security Agency?

453
00:24:59,020 --> 00:25:00,060
Listen carefully.

454
00:25:00,380 --> 00:25:02,460
Except those disgraced scholars,

455
00:25:02,540 --> 00:25:04,700
take some others back

456
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:05,820
as witnesses.

457
00:25:05,900 --> 00:25:06,740
Aye.

458
00:25:15,220 --> 00:25:16,740
I heard Deputy Officer Yang

459
00:25:16,740 --> 00:25:18,260
took his men to Winehouse Fan,

460
00:25:18,580 --> 00:25:19,980
saying scholars were going to rebel.

461
00:25:22,580 --> 00:25:24,140
All right, I see.

462
00:25:31,220 --> 00:25:32,340
Ridiculous!

463
00:25:33,420 --> 00:25:35,340
How can such scholars rebel?

464
00:25:36,220 --> 00:25:37,700
Those scholars talk wildly

465
00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:38,940
because they’re unsatisfied with

466
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:40,220
recent situation.

467
00:25:40,340 --> 00:25:42,460
I’m afraid someone wants to

468
00:25:42,460 --> 00:25:44,820
suppress those reform officials.

469
00:25:46,060 --> 00:25:47,300
Shall we report to His Majesty now?

470
00:25:47,940 --> 00:25:49,180
The Eighth Princess is critically ill.

471
00:25:49,340 --> 00:25:51,100
His Majesty is in the Pavilion of Luan now.

472
00:25:52,180 --> 00:25:53,060
Let’s go to tell Her Highness.

473
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:57,420
How can we get Her Highness involved?

474
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:01,220
Will His Majesty punish those scholars?

475
00:26:08,620 --> 00:26:10,380
This is not what I should worry about

476
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:13,020
as a eunuch.

477
00:26:14,700 --> 00:26:15,900
Do you only

478
00:26:16,500 --> 00:26:17,540
care about one person?

479
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:24,500
I don’t think

480
00:26:24,500 --> 00:26:25,780
Yang Huaimin will come back tonight.

481
00:26:27,540 --> 00:26:28,700
I can just check up on him.

482
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:32,220
That year when the Fourth Princess
was suddenly ill,

483
00:26:32,540 --> 00:26:33,460
one maid

484
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:35,540
jumped into the lake and died,

485
00:26:36,060 --> 00:26:37,980
and the other maid ran out of the palace.

486
00:26:39,020 --> 00:26:40,500
Can’t Imperial Security Agency

487
00:26:40,700 --> 00:26:41,900
find an escaped maid

488
00:26:41,900 --> 00:26:43,100
in such a long time?

489
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:49,300
Let’s go to Imperial Security Agency.

490
00:27:36,940 --> 00:27:38,180
Leave me alone.

491
00:27:38,620 --> 00:27:39,860
Get in to take care of Madam Zhang.

492
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:43,820
She doesn’t allow anyone else to get in,

493
00:27:44,340 --> 00:27:46,140
except Aunt Jia.

494
00:27:47,460 --> 00:27:48,940
I don’t dare to annoy her.

495
00:27:52,580 --> 00:27:53,820
Just wait there, then.

496
00:27:55,220 --> 00:27:56,420
Aunt Jia is getting old.

497
00:27:56,420 --> 00:27:57,260
She...

498
00:27:59,860 --> 00:28:01,660
She isn’t very considerate.

499
00:28:04,260 --> 00:28:05,180
Go to wait out there.

500
00:28:05,620 --> 00:28:07,620
Let me know if anything happens.

501
00:28:09,660 --> 00:28:11,220
I’m kind of relieved

502
00:28:12,540 --> 00:28:13,580
when you take care of Madam Zhang.

503
00:28:18,580 --> 00:28:20,340
Today, Mr. Cao played a Hou Yi.

504
00:28:20,500 --> 00:28:21,940
He is even more handsome

505
00:28:22,060 --> 00:28:23,300
than the one in the painting.

506
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:28,100
My nephew...

507
00:28:29,140 --> 00:28:30,580
Since he was little, he’s been handsome

508
00:28:30,580 --> 00:28:31,620
and smart.

509
00:28:32,340 --> 00:28:34,060
All seniors favor him.

510
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:35,900
People cluster around him wherever he goes.

511
00:28:36,860 --> 00:28:38,660
My brother took him at work.

512
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:40,700
My brother isn’t strict

513
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:41,740
and seldom restrains him.

514
00:28:42,220 --> 00:28:43,700
Now, he’s fourteen or fifteen years old.

515
00:28:44,220 --> 00:28:46,260
He’s impetuous and doesn’t study well.

516
00:28:46,580 --> 00:28:49,020
I don’t think he learns martial arts carefully.

517
00:28:49,700 --> 00:28:50,780
But he has attracted

518
00:28:50,780 --> 00:28:52,700
many girls.

519
00:28:54,380 --> 00:28:55,660
Your Highness.

520
00:28:55,660 --> 00:28:56,820
You’re too strict with your nephew.

521
00:28:57,540 --> 00:28:59,380
I heard Junior Cao is good at

522
00:28:59,380 --> 00:29:01,420
riding, shooting and music.

523
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:03,220
He’s a fantastic young man.

524
00:29:03,660 --> 00:29:05,500
I saw the immortal he played today.

525
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:07,380
He looked much cooler

526
00:29:07,540 --> 00:29:08,580
than the painted figures.

527
00:29:11,060 --> 00:29:11,780
Qiuhe.

528
00:29:13,060 --> 00:29:14,660
I thought you were young,

529
00:29:14,660 --> 00:29:15,540
but prudent.

530
00:29:16,020 --> 00:29:17,860
How could you also like those naive girls?

531
00:29:21,260 --> 00:29:21,940
Okay.

532
00:29:23,220 --> 00:29:24,580
If you really like him,

533
00:29:24,580 --> 00:29:25,860
I can at least help you

534
00:29:26,100 --> 00:29:27,380
as his aunt.

535
00:29:28,220 --> 00:29:30,100
Tomorrow, I’ll ask His Majesty

536
00:29:30,260 --> 00:29:32,380
to marry you to my nephew Cao Ping.

537
00:29:33,380 --> 00:29:34,500
He’s not a bad man.

538
00:29:34,500 --> 00:29:35,460
He’s just impetuous.

539
00:29:36,020 --> 00:29:36,900
If a wise wife like you

540
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:38,980
can stay and remind him,

541
00:29:39,980 --> 00:29:41,380
maybe he can calm down

542
00:29:41,500 --> 00:29:43,180
and study hard.

543
00:29:44,620 --> 00:29:45,500
Your Highness.

544
00:29:45,860 --> 00:29:47,740
I just admire

545
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:48,620
his performance.

546
00:29:49,140 --> 00:29:50,420
I don’t dare to marry him.

547
00:29:55,860 --> 00:29:56,700
Stand up.

548
00:29:59,260 --> 00:30:00,340
Silly girl.

549
00:30:01,860 --> 00:30:03,100
Since I promised you,

550
00:30:03,860 --> 00:30:06,100
I’ll marry you to someone you want.

551
00:30:10,180 --> 00:30:11,980
But the prince died young.

552
00:30:12,100 --> 00:30:13,300
The Eighth Princess is critically ill.

553
00:30:14,260 --> 00:30:16,060
His Majesty is really sad.

554
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:17,140
Last time, he...

555
00:30:17,340 --> 00:30:18,060
Your Highness.

556
00:30:18,060 --> 00:30:19,500
Don’t ask His Majesty

557
00:30:19,500 --> 00:30:21,020
to allow me to leave the palace earlier.

558
00:30:21,740 --> 00:30:22,820
It’s only two years

559
00:30:22,820 --> 00:30:23,940
before I leave.

560
00:30:24,620 --> 00:30:26,500
I think it’s a short time

561
00:30:26,860 --> 00:30:28,100
and I will miss you.

562
00:30:29,820 --> 00:30:30,540
Silly girl.

563
00:30:31,260 --> 00:30:32,740
Can you stay with me all your life?

564
00:30:53,540 --> 00:30:55,660
All girls pray to the moon on Mid-autumn Festival

565
00:30:58,620 --> 00:31:00,740
to be as beautiful as Chang’e

566
00:31:01,540 --> 00:31:02,700
and to have a good husband.

567
00:31:05,860 --> 00:31:07,700
Chang’e was beautiful

568
00:31:08,100 --> 00:31:09,180
and she married

569
00:31:09,180 --> 00:31:10,500
the world’s bravest hero.

570
00:31:10,540 --> 00:31:11,780
So what?

571
00:31:15,260 --> 00:31:16,860
When I was little, I didn’t understand

572
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:20,300
why she stole double elixirs

573
00:31:21,860 --> 00:31:23,700
and spent the endless life

574
00:31:24,740 --> 00:31:27,340
in the Moon Palace alone

575
00:31:28,420 --> 00:31:30,100
instead of staying with her hero husband

576
00:31:31,260 --> 00:31:34,140
and loving each other.

577
00:31:37,780 --> 00:31:39,380
Hou Yi was a good man.

578
00:31:40,700 --> 00:31:42,300
But maybe Chang’e didn’t love him.

579
00:31:45,060 --> 00:31:46,740
Common people are jealous of the imperial family.

580
00:31:49,380 --> 00:31:50,780
Mortals are jealous of the immortals.

581
00:31:53,620 --> 00:31:54,540
People are jealous

582
00:31:56,420 --> 00:31:58,500
only because they don’t know what others suffer.

583
00:32:27,460 --> 00:32:28,220
Huaiji.

584
00:32:30,340 --> 00:32:31,180
- Stand up. - I...

585
00:32:41,180 --> 00:32:41,940
Look.

586
00:32:43,340 --> 00:32:44,500
This is the bamboo cage

587
00:32:45,100 --> 00:32:46,460
I made for Zuixinglai.

588
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:49,420
I just finished it.

589
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:54,420
Let’s go catch some flying crickets.

590
00:32:54,940 --> 00:32:56,060
Zuixinglai likes them.

591
00:33:00,700 --> 00:33:01,860
I should catch more.

592
00:33:04,300 --> 00:33:05,740
Maybe Chuyue and Yaoyao

593
00:33:10,020 --> 00:33:11,140
also like them.

594
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:41,900
People were sent

595
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:42,860
to check up on that maid.

596
00:33:43,540 --> 00:33:45,420
But no one tracked her down.

597
00:33:46,500 --> 00:33:47,940
It wasn’t solved in months.

598
00:33:48,540 --> 00:33:50,340
Yet there were no notes.

599
00:33:51,500 --> 00:33:52,900
No more guys were sent.

600
00:33:53,700 --> 00:33:55,220
Nothing was even recorded.

601
00:33:57,220 --> 00:33:58,820
Yang Huaimin doesn’t

602
00:33:58,820 --> 00:34:00,020
care for Madam Zhang

603
00:34:00,540 --> 00:34:02,980
as much as His Majesty or Madam Zhang

604
00:34:02,980 --> 00:34:04,820
thinks he does.

605
00:34:07,380 --> 00:34:08,540
You mean

606
00:34:08,860 --> 00:34:10,020
he and Xu Lantiao

607
00:34:10,500 --> 00:34:12,940
are not loyal to Madam Zhang?

608
00:34:17,060 --> 00:34:18,540
What about Xia Song?

609
00:34:24,340 --> 00:34:25,060
Liaozi.

610
00:34:27,140 --> 00:34:28,380
Pay more attention

611
00:34:29,900 --> 00:34:31,180
to Zhang Chengzhao.

612
00:34:43,140 --> 00:34:44,540
Oh, it’s already autumn.

613
00:34:48,540 --> 00:34:50,140
And there are no flying crickets.

614
00:34:51,620 --> 00:34:53,420
There will be some next year.

615
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:55,420
Next year?

616
00:35:00,020 --> 00:35:00,980
Huaiji.

617
00:35:03,100 --> 00:35:04,140
When you were little,

618
00:35:05,020 --> 00:35:07,340
did your father take you to catch crickets

619
00:35:07,620 --> 00:35:08,660
or cicadas?

620
00:35:10,980 --> 00:35:11,860
My...

621
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:16,140
My father died

622
00:35:16,820 --> 00:35:19,780
soon after I was born.

623
00:35:21,340 --> 00:35:24,660
Later, my elder brother worked as an apprentice.

624
00:35:26,380 --> 00:35:29,630
Mother worked every day to make a living,

625
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:33,020
expecting me to study well.

626
00:35:34,780 --> 00:35:35,980
Except reading,

627
00:35:36,940 --> 00:35:38,980
I only helped mother with trifles.

628
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:41,820
I never had fun

629
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:43,140
catching insects or fishes.

630
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:50,620
Yeah.

631
00:35:52,740 --> 00:35:55,060
In common families,

632
00:35:55,820 --> 00:35:57,220
most parents

633
00:35:58,140 --> 00:36:00,220
have to work every day

634
00:36:00,220 --> 00:36:01,500
to make a living.

635
00:36:02,580 --> 00:36:04,460
Few of them are free enough

636
00:36:04,860 --> 00:36:06,500
to have fun with their children.

637
00:36:10,700 --> 00:36:13,940
At least,

638
00:36:15,740 --> 00:36:17,500
Zuixinglai, Yaoyao and Chuyue

639
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:18,460
lived a rich and carefree life.

640
00:36:19,980 --> 00:36:20,900
I thought

641
00:36:22,620 --> 00:36:23,980
they were the poorest children

642
00:36:23,980 --> 00:36:25,260
in this world

643
00:36:26,300 --> 00:36:28,060
and I was the most unfortunate father.

644
00:36:31,220 --> 00:36:32,900
I was too narrow.

645
00:36:36,820 --> 00:36:37,980
I lost my father.

646
00:36:39,500 --> 00:36:40,660
But when my mother was alive,

647
00:36:41,540 --> 00:36:42,700
we lived a happy life.

648
00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:45,660
My neighbors and relatives

649
00:36:46,820 --> 00:36:47,900
weren’t very rich.

650
00:36:49,140 --> 00:36:52,940
They worked hard, but lived in harmony.

651
00:36:55,740 --> 00:36:57,660
Some uncles and aunts often said

652
00:36:58,420 --> 00:36:59,580
we were lucky enough

653
00:37:00,300 --> 00:37:01,700
to live in a flourishing age.

654
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:03,980
But...

655
00:37:08,740 --> 00:37:10,140
then a pestilence broke out.

656
00:37:16,420 --> 00:37:17,460
Pestilence?

657
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:36,540
Pestilence.

658
00:37:43,460 --> 00:37:44,820
Life is always changeable.

659
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:48,740
Who can get rid of the pain

660
00:37:51,060 --> 00:37:52,740
in life and death?

661
00:37:57,220 --> 00:37:58,780
Despite of fate,

662
00:37:59,820 --> 00:38:01,580
we still have to try,

663
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:04,940
even for some peace

664
00:38:06,595 --> 00:38:08,125
in a short time.

665
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:20,660
I’ve got some files to review.

666
00:38:21,660 --> 00:38:22,460
Huaiji.

667
00:38:24,580 --> 00:38:25,540
From tomorrow on,

668
00:38:26,220 --> 00:38:27,500
come back with me.

669
00:38:29,220 --> 00:38:30,580
I didn’t get you back,

670
00:38:33,980 --> 00:38:35,900
because you might remind me of Zuixinglai

671
00:38:37,140 --> 00:38:38,140
and I would be sad.

672
00:38:41,180 --> 00:38:42,780
But I must review proposals

673
00:38:43,620 --> 00:38:44,820
and I must work.

674
00:38:48,020 --> 00:38:53,340
Zuixinglai is in my heart.

675
00:38:54,980 --> 00:38:56,460
It’s my luck

676
00:38:59,380 --> 00:39:00,620
when I often think of him.

677
00:39:16,740 --> 00:39:20,180
Su Shunqin criticized current affairs in public,

678
00:39:21,300 --> 00:39:24,540
saying you were hesitant

679
00:39:24,540 --> 00:39:25,620
and undetermined.

680
00:39:25,700 --> 00:39:27,340
Cheated by evil guys,

681
00:39:28,020 --> 00:39:30,700
you transferred Fan Zhongyan and Fu Bi away,

682
00:39:30,700 --> 00:39:34,220
just like demotion.

683
00:39:34,700 --> 00:39:36,700
He... He said you were fatuous.

684
00:39:37,020 --> 00:39:37,860
How dare you!

685
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:48,180
Did Su Shunqin say

686
00:39:49,940 --> 00:39:51,780
the word fatuous?

687
00:39:52,460 --> 00:39:54,340
Su... Su Shunqin...

688
00:39:55,140 --> 00:39:57,540
He... He despised His Majesty

689
00:39:58,100 --> 00:39:59,700
and said disrespectful words.

690
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:00,660
Don’t talk nonsense.

691
00:40:02,580 --> 00:40:03,500
I asked.

692
00:40:05,180 --> 00:40:07,060
Did Su Shunqin say the word

693
00:40:07,060 --> 00:40:08,020
fatuous?

694
00:40:09,420 --> 00:40:10,340
If he didn’t,

695
00:40:11,100 --> 00:40:12,340
you said it then.

696
00:40:12,340 --> 00:40:12,900
I... I...

697
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:14,060
You’re insulting His Majesty.

698
00:40:14,820 --> 00:40:16,060
How... How could I?

699
00:40:16,420 --> 00:40:17,700
He... he said that.

700
00:40:19,020 --> 00:40:20,100
Think carefully of it.

701
00:40:20,700 --> 00:40:22,260
When you confront each other,

702
00:40:22,860 --> 00:40:23,940
if he didn’t say it,

703
00:40:24,940 --> 00:40:27,140
you must be slandering him

704
00:40:27,140 --> 00:40:28,140
and cheating His Majesty.

705
00:40:35,780 --> 00:40:38,660
Mr. Han, isn’t that ridiculous

706
00:40:39,780 --> 00:40:41,220
when you find fault with one word?

707
00:40:44,180 --> 00:40:46,660
I’m not being ridiculous.

708
00:40:48,620 --> 00:40:51,780
Your Majesty, scholars care about politics.

709
00:40:52,540 --> 00:40:53,580
When they talk,

710
00:40:54,220 --> 00:40:56,180
many of them sound indignant.

711
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:59,580
But they only commend on affairs.

712
00:41:00,740 --> 00:41:01,900
Su Shunqin and the others

713
00:41:02,420 --> 00:41:03,940
are honest and less considerate.

714
00:41:04,740 --> 00:41:06,260
When they offer advice to You Majesty,

715
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,420
they are always intense, too.

716
00:41:09,700 --> 00:41:11,540
But no matter they’re right or wrong,

717
00:41:12,540 --> 00:41:14,500
they never go beyond the limits.

718
00:41:15,500 --> 00:41:16,740
If they humiliate you

719
00:41:17,540 --> 00:41:19,420
with the word fatuous,

720
00:41:20,380 --> 00:41:21,780
they must be insulting you.

721
00:41:22,300 --> 00:41:23,460
Whoever said that

722
00:41:24,220 --> 00:41:25,500
could even be executed.

723
00:41:27,220 --> 00:41:27,940
I...

724
00:41:34,060 --> 00:41:37,500
Your Majesty, in the interrogation last night,

725
00:41:38,220 --> 00:41:39,540
Su Shunqin admitted

726
00:41:39,540 --> 00:41:40,740
= Yang Huaimin =
he talked about politics in public

727
00:41:41,140 --> 00:41:43,180
and disliked the transfer of Fan and Fu,

728
00:41:43,340 --> 00:41:44,140
thinking you weren’t determined

729
00:41:44,140 --> 00:41:46,340
in supporting the reform.

730
00:41:47,500 --> 00:41:48,300
But...

731
00:41:48,620 --> 00:41:51,580
he didn’t say the word fatuous.

732
00:41:53,020 --> 00:41:55,100
Su Shunqin complained quite a lot.

733
00:41:55,420 --> 00:41:57,780
He was unsatisfied with you and politics.

734
00:41:58,500 --> 00:42:04,300
Maybe Li Ding remembered something wrong.

735
00:42:18,300 --> 00:42:22,620
= Wang Gongchen, courtesy name Junkuang =

